  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 47a621783cb453147b01764dde5ed130, type: 3}
  m_Name: 0_Intro
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPCDialogue
  dialogueLines:
  - My dear,
  - If you are reading this, then I have already gone where the moonlight carries
    us all in the end...
  - I know this cottage must seem strange to you now...
  - Old. Forgotten. Perhaps even a burden. But it has been waiting for you longer
    than you realize.
  - The pendant I left you will guide you when the time is right. Trust it.
  - And trust yourself, even when the nights grow unfamiliar.
  - Beyond these walls lies a place tied to our family for generations.
  - A place that needs gentle hands and a patient heart...
  - I am sorry I could not tell you everything sooner. But the moon always reveals
    what daylight hides.
  - 'With all my love, Grandma Selene. '
